item.title: Final Remarks
item.description: Link The Plan Today I couldn’t end this series without saying a few final remarks, so here we are! It’s been a long and rewarding journey of learning and adapting, so I wanted to summarize a few of the top lessons learned, give thanks, and look forward. Link Final Remarks I’ve learned a lot this semester, and much of it has been through guided trial-and-error. Looking back, I feel very proud of all the work I’ve done, and how accurate my models were, especially given that they were my first real shots at forecasting U.
